---
// Landing A
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Otwarty Sklep — Twój sklep widoczny dla AI</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:opsz,wght@14..32,300..800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    color: hsl(0 0% 9%);
    background: hsl(0 0% 100%);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
    font-optical-sizing: auto;
    font-feature-settings: 'cv01', 'cv02', 'ss01';
    hanging-punctuation: first allow-end last;
  }

  .page {
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 24px 72px;
  }

  /* --- top --- */
  .top {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid hsl(0 0% 9%);
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }
  .logo {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .tag {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: hsl(0 0% 45%);
  }

  /* --- h1 shadcn-style --- */
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5.5vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    text-wrap: balance;
    color: hsl(0 0% 4%);
  }

  /* --- marker --- */
  mark {
    background: transparent;
    color: inherit;
    background-image: linear-gradient(120deg, hsl(50 100% 80%) 0%, hsl(50 100% 70%) 100%);
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: 100% 40%;
    background-position: 0 85%;
    padding: 0 2px;
  }

  /* --- lead / intro --- */
  .lead {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    letter-spacing: -0.011em;
    color: hsl(0 0% 45%);
    margin-bottom: 72px;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  /* --- grid --- */
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 36px 1fr;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
    border-top: 1.5px solid hsl(0 0% 9%);
  }
  .grid-num {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 20px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid hsl(0 0% 90%);
    color: hsl(0 0% 45%);
    font-variant-numeric: lining-nums tabular-nums;
  }
  .grid-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-weight: 400;
    padding: 20px 0 20px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid hsl(0 0% 90%);
    color: hsl(0 0% 9%);
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  /* --- form --- */
  .form-section {
    border-top: 1.5px solid hsl(0 0% 9%);
    padding-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }
  .form-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.011em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: hsl(0 0% 9%);
  }
  form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    max-width: 460px;
  }
  input[type="email"] {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border: 1.5px solid hsl(0 0% 9%);
    border-right: none;
    border-radius: 6px 0 0 6px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-family: inherit;
    letter-spacing: -0.011em;
    outline: none;
    background: hsl(0 0% 100%);
    color: hsl(0 0% 9%);
    transition: box-shadow 0.15s;
  }
  input[type="email"]::placeholder { color: hsl(0 0% 64%); }
  input[type="email"]:focus { box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px hsl(0 0% 80%); }
  button {
    background: hsl(0 0% 9%);
    color: hsl(0 0% 98%);
    border: 1.5px solid hsl(0 0% 9%);
    border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: inherit;
    letter-spacing: -0.011em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  button:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
  .form-note {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: hsl(0 0% 45%);
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  /* --- channels --- */
  .channels {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }
  .channel {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: hsl(0 0% 78%);
  }

  /* --- stat --- */
  .stat {
    border-top: 1px solid hsl(0 0% 90%);
    padding-top: 28px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 28px;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: hsl(0 0% 4%);
    font-variant-numeric: lining-nums tabular-nums;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: hsl(0 0% 45%);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .page { padding: 48px 20px 48px; }
    .top { margin-bottom: 56px; }
    h1 { margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .lead { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .grid { margin-bottom: 48px; }
    form { flex-direction: column; }
    input[type="email"] { border-right: 1.5px solid hsl(0 0% 9%); border-bottom: none; border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0; }
    button { border-radius: 0 0 6px 6px; width: 100%; }
    .stat { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <div class="top">
    <div class="logo">Otwarty Sklep</div>
    <div class="tag">Early Access</div>
  </div>

  <h1>Twój sklep jest <mark>niewidoczny</mark> dla AI</h1>

  <p class="lead">
    ChatGPT, Google AI i Von Halsky obsługują miliony zapytań zakupowych dziennie.
    Twoje produkty tam nie istnieją. Podłączamy Twój sklep do AI agentów
    — <mark>bez zmiany czegokolwiek</mark>.
  </p>

  <div class="grid">
    <div class="grid-num">01</div>
    <div class="grid-text">Mirror Twojego sklepu w formacie zrozumiałym dla AI agentów. <mark>Bez migracji</mark>, bez pluginów</div>
    <div class="grid-num">02</div>
    <div class="grid-text">Produkty widoczne w ChatGPT Shopping, Google AI Mode i <mark>Von Halsky — 16 mln klientów</mark> InPostu</div>
    <div class="grid-num">03</div>
    <div class="grid-text">Setup w 24 godziny. <mark>Od 29 zł miesięcznie</mark>. Rezygnujesz kiedy chcesz</div>
  </div>

  <div class="form-section">
    <div class="form-label">Zostaw email — odezwiemy się w 48h</div>
    <form action="https://formspree.io/f/TWOJ_ID" method="POST">
      <input type="hidden" name="_landing" value="A-mirror">
      <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="twoj@email.pl" required>
      <button type="submit">Chcę early access</button>
    </form>
    <div class="form-note">Bez spamu. Odpisujemy osobiście.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="channels">
    <span class="channel">UCP</span>
    <span class="channel">Google AI</span>
    <span class="channel">ChatGPT</span>
    <span class="channel">Von Halsky</span>
  </div>

  <div class="stat">
    <div>
      <div class="stat-num">25 000</div>
      <div class="stat-label">polskich sklepów przeskanowanych</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="stat-num">95%</div>
      <div class="stat-label">niewidocznych dla AI agentów</div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
